  i  thank  the  prime  minister  and  the  minister  of urban  development  for  implementing  two  important  schemes  namely  smart  city project and atal mission for rejuvenation and urban transformation ie amrut urban infrastructural facilities are facing the burden of exodus at large scale in my constituency jalgaon at present there are 5828 slum clusters having a population of about 30000 these people have no access to any kind of civic amenities like potable water or toilets etc i urge upon the government to coordinate with the government of maharashtra and execute housing project under amrut scheme in jalgaon town and take necessary action for relocation of these slum dwellers so that the standard to living of these people could be raised   